<HEAD>RETRANSMITTING FOR ALL NEEDING</HEAD>
<HEAD>The Year in Trivia: I'll Never Forget What's-Its-Face</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDS: CORRECTS question 15 by changing Zinsen to Zinser, answer 11
by changing James to John Wesley Fletcher, answer 14 by changing
Pete du Pont to Alexander Haig.</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By SCOTT WILLIAMS</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
 What do you remember about 1988?
</TEXT>
