 </LOCATION> <LOCATION> York </LOCATION> firm. `` The people I've spoken to have indicated their support.'' Among the staunch supporters have been such small, growth-oriented companies as <LOCATION> Red </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Bank </LOCATION>, <LOCATION> N.J. </LOCATION>, real estate developer <ORGANIZATION> Hovnanian </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Enterprises </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION> `` We feel indebted to <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION>,'' said Hovnanian President <PERSON> Ara </PERSON> <PERSON> Hovnanian </PERSON>. `` They helped us a great deal with our financing and that's why we'll be standing with them in their difficult times.'' <ORGANIZATION> Hovnanian </ORGANIZATION> said <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION>'s $ 100 million in junk bonds enabled it grow more than six-fold over the past six year. <PERSON> Thomas </PERSON> <PERSON> Reed </PERSON>, spokesman for <ORGANIZATION> Shamrock </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Holdings </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>, which hopes to take over <ORGANIZATION> Polaroid </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Corp. </ORGANIZATION> with the help of <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION> junk-bond financing, said his firm would maintain its relationship with <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION>. `` Shamrock is gratified that <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION>'s put the whole thing behind them. It's been a very difficult experience, but it resolves any uncertainties, real or imagined, that may have existed on Wall Street concerning <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION>'s ability to operate,'' <PERSON> Reed </PERSON> said. <PERSON> Harold </PERSON> <PERSON> Simmons </PERSON>, billionaire chairman of Dallas-based <ORGANIZATION> Valhi </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Inc. </ORGANIZATION>, was equally as supportive. <PERSON> Simmons </PERSON> said he used <ORGANIZATION> Drexel </ORGANIZATION> to float junk bonds three times, most recently in February when he increased his stake in <ORGANIZATION> NL </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Industries </ORGANIZATION>, a company of which he is now chairman. `` I'm sure we'll be doing business with them in the future,'' he said.
